<title>USA: KLLM adopts shareholder rights plan.</title>
<headline>KLLM adopts shareholder rights plan.</headline>
<dateline>JACKSON, Miss. 1997-02-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>KLLM Transport Services Inc said its board adopted a stockholder rights plan at its regular meeting today.</p>
<p>The company said the plan is designed to enable KLLM and its board to enhance value so that all stockholders can realize the long-term value of their investment in KLLM.</p>
<p>The plan is also intended to protect stockholders in the event an attempt is made to acquire control of the company through certain coercive or unfair tactics.</p>
